"true">#</span></a></h2><p>The BigQuery backend is a more robust and scalab=
le backend option that is battle-tested and production ready. Use this back=
end if you intend to have heavy logging usage and require advanced querying=
 features such as the Logs Explorer.</p><h3 id=3D"configuration-and-require=
ments" class=3D"group scroll-mt-24">Configuration and Requirements<a href=
